caption:
Disc golf putter dialed for 2024? 

Be 200% ready for the new season with this Disc Golf Putting Master Class with Kristofer Hivju and 6x World Champion Paul “Michaelangelo” McBeth. 

The 2024 Disc Golf Pro Tour starts TODAY at the Chess.com Invitational on the Paul McBeth designed Olympus course in Florida. Don’t miss it! 

…and you better believe there’ll be more fun stuff from this dynamic duo in the months to come. Make sure to follow our channels!

DREAM DAY WITH THE G.O.A.T.

We finally got the opportunity to challenge the greatest disc golfer of all time - Paul McBeth! The reigning - and six times World Champion. How we did? Well, let’s just say there’s some fun stuff to watch coming up. 🔥
